# Include any files or directories that you don't want to be copied to your
# container here (e.g., local build artifacts, temporary files, etc.).
#
# For more help, visit the .dockerignore file reference guide at
# https://docs.docker.com/go/build-context-dockerignore/

**/.DS_Store
**/__pycache__
**/.venv
**/.classpath
**/.dockerignore
**/.env
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.project
**/.settings
**/.toolstarget
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/*.*proj.user
**/*.dbmdl
**/*.jfm
**/bin
**/charts
**/docker-compose*
**/compose.y*ml
**/Dockerfile*
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log
**/obj
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/values.dev.yaml
LICENSE
README.md


# --- Python & Build Artifacts ---
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/env/
**/venv/
**/requirements.txt
**/requirements_dev.txt

# --- Project-Specific Secrets & Data ---
# These are handled by Docker Secrets or mounted volumes, NOT the image.
**/secrets/
**/db/*.sql

# --- Windows System Junk ---
[Cc]ache/
[Tt]humbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*.lnk
*.exe
*.dll
*.msi

# --- IDE & Developer Tools ---
# Based on your "Task Tracker.code-workspace" and "to_do.txt" files.
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.code-workspace
**/to_do.txt
**/.history/
